ed magnetic shear in the corona by the reconnection process\nexplains the descending motion of the LT source. During the second phase, the\nordinary reconnection process dominates describing the energy release in terms\nof the standard model of large eruptive flares.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Sep 2008 10:52:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 13 Nov 2009 11:01:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
